s://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/268245/', '', 'Gemfibrozil, Fenofibric acid, Mipomersen, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Dextrothyroxine, Probucol, Cholestyramine, Clofibrate, Colestipol, Niacin, More', 'Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, Cerivastatin, Colesevelam, Alirocumab', 1767369485);
